144
00:06:12,480 --> 00:06:14,320
and not much is happening,

145
00:06:14,320 --> 00:06:16,460
other than microscopically,

146
00:06:16,460 --> 00:06:16,940
of course.

147
00:06:19,360 --> 00:06:21,060
That's a state of thermal equilibrium.

148
00:06:21,440 --> 00:06:23,140
In a state of thermal equilibrium,

149
00:06:23,140 --> 00:06:25,220
heat tends not to flow.

150
00:06:25,460 --> 00:06:26,140
We will see,

151
00:06:26,140 --> 00:06:27,560
we'll understand that soon enough.

152
00:06:28,340 --> 00:06:31,210
Heat tends not to flow because all

153
00:06:31,210 --> 00:06:34,080
