154
00:06:37,479 --> 00:06:38,080
And,

155
00:06:38,080 --> 00:06:39,740
as I say,

156
00:06:39,740 --> 00:06:40,440
as we will see,

157
00:06:40,440 --> 00:06:46,660
the probability distributions for given average energy do,

158
00:06:46,660 --> 00:06:47,300
in fact,

159
00:06:47,300 --> 00:06:49,200
tend to broaden and broaden and

160
00:06:49,200 --> 00:06:51,100
broaden as the energy goes up,

161
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:53,880
so that the entropy is

162
00:06:53,880 --> 00:06:56,520
a monotonically increasing function of energy.

163
00:06:57,640 --> 00:06:58,540
Important fact.

164
00:07:00,080 --> 00:07:00,640
Okay,

