183
00:07:48,940 --> 00:07:49,620
Now,

184
00:07:49,620 --> 00:07:50,680
what on earth does that mean?

185
00:07:51,860 --> 00:07:55,570
What it means is if you have

186
00:07:55,570 --> 00:07:59,280
a system described by a given probability distribution,

187
00:08:00,320 --> 00:08:02,360
and it's not in equilibrium,

