215
00:09:06,720 --> 00:09:08,820
exactly the opposite tends to happen.

216
00:09:08,840 --> 00:09:11,460
You lose track of things.

217
00:09:11,920 --> 00:09:14,300
And because you lose track of things,

218
00:09:15,280 --> 00:09:20,000
