00:11:14,660 --> 00:11:16,810
That the energy flow is

267
00:11:16,810 --> 00:11:18,960
from larger temperature to smaller temperature,

268
00:11:19,760 --> 00:11:20,840
number one.

269
00:11:21,860 --> 00:11:23,000
And number two,

