00:11:52,620 --> 00:11:54,230
until the lower temperature one becomes

284
00:11:54,230 --> 00:11:55,840
hotter than the higher temperature one.

285
00:11:56,360 --> 00:11:58,620
But then the energy will flow back the other way.

286
00:11:58,680 --> 00:11:58,840
Well,

287
00:11:58,840 --> 00:11:59,620
that's not what happens.

