00:19:40,200 --> 00:19:41,340
and see where they lead.

483
00:19:41,860 --> 00:19:42,560
All right?

484
00:19:42,640 --> 00:19:42,940
So,

485
00:19:42,940 --> 00:19:44,920
we have

486
00:19:46,240 --> 00:19:47,520
SA and SB,

487
00:19:47,780 --> 00:19:48,680
dS A,

488
00:19:48,680 --> 00:19:49,280
dS B,

489
00:19:49,420 --> 00:19:50,180
but they're connected,

