00:19:51,860 --> 00:19:53,700
and rewrite this inequality.

492
00:19:54,880 --> 00:19:55,460
So,

493
00:19:55,460 --> 00:19:56,540
we rewrite the inequality.

494
00:19:56,840 --> 00:19:59,580
It's dS A plus,

