00:20:13,899 --> 00:20:16,200
and that's greater than zero.

501
00:20:16,440 --> 00:20:18,400
That's what the second law tells us.

502
00:20:21,480 --> 00:20:23,920
Allow me to multiply it by TB

503
00:20:23,920 --> 00:20:24,940
for simplicity.

504
00:20:25,080 --> 00:20:26,940
Let's just multiply it by TB.

505
00:20:30,000 --> 00:20:32,360
We will assume temperatures are positive,

506
00:20:33,280 --> 00:20:34,540
unless otherwise,

507
00:20:35,399 --> 00:20:37,620
there are situations in which temperature

508
00:20:37,620 --> 00:20:38,300
can be negative,

