00:21:12,280 --> 00:21:14,860
then TB minus TA is positive.

526
00:21:17,020 --> 00:21:18,900
What does that say about dS A?

527
00:21:19,240 --> 00:21:20,720
A positive number

528
00:21:21,300 --> 00:21:22,420
times the change

529
00:21:23,150 --> 00:21:24,300
in the A entropy

