00:21:24,300 --> 00:21:25,480
is positive.

531
00:21:26,360 --> 00:21:29,560
That says that dS A is positive.

532
00:21:32,030 --> 00:21:32,380
So,

533
00:21:34,580 --> 00:21:36,800
what we conclude from this equation,

534
00:21:40,120 --> 00:21:44,360
is that dS A for the particular setup up there,

